Anteater Poker

a fun for the whole family online poker game!

Contents:
- `bin/` - prebuilt programs and runtime assets
- `bin/poker_server` - server with GUI monitor
- `bin/poker_server_headless` - server without GUI monitor
- `bin/poker_client` - client program
- `doc/` - `Poker_UserManual.pdf`
- `COPYRIGHT` - licensing and ownership
- `INSTALL` - quick run instructions

To run:
  cd bin
  ./poker_server

Then open another terminal:
  cd bin
  ./poker_client

The server uses port 10160 by default. For complete gameplay, connection
instructions, and rules, see `doc/Poker_UserManual.pdf`.

Authors: team 16 (99%)
Version: V1.0, 2026-06-07
